// Tessera 改色插件提示（Dark Reader 等）
// 与开屏模块同宽对齐；默认隐藏，由 JS 加 .drn-show 显示
#dark-reader-notice
  display: none
  margin: 0 auto
  padding: 96px 15px 0
  max-width: 1400px
  width: 100%

  // 与 #home-top 同步：超大屏跟随 .layout 收到 60% 视口宽
  +minWidth2000()
    max-width: 60%

  +maxWidth768()
    padding: 90px 12px 0

  &.drn-show
    display: block

  .drn-inner
    @extend .cardHover
    display: flex
    align-items: center
    gap: 14px
    padding: 14px 16px

  .drn-icon
    flex: 0 0 auto
    font-size: 22px
    color: var(--tessera-primary)

  .drn-text
    display: flex
    flex-direction: column
    gap: 3px
    flex: 1 1 auto
    min-width: 0

  .drn-title
    font-weight: 600
    // 显式行高：否则标题继承全局较大行高，首行上方留白会比末行下方多，导致上下不对称
    line-height: 1.5
    color: var(--font-color)

  .drn-desc
    font-size: 13px
    line-height: 1.6
    color: var(--text-highlight-color)
    opacity: .85

  .drn-close
    display: flex
    align-items: center
    justify-content: center
    flex: 0 0 auto
    width: 32px
    height: 32px
    color: var(--font-color)
    background: transparent
    font-size: 15px
    cursor: pointer
    addBorderRadius(8)
    transition: background-color .3s ease, color .3s ease

    &:hover
      background: var(--tessera-primary)
      color: #fff

// 提示显示时，下方模块无需再为贴顶导航栏留出整段高度
#dark-reader-notice.drn-show ~ #home-top
  padding-top: 24px

#dark-reader-notice.drn-show ~ .layout
  padding-top: 24px
